summary: This document appears to be a cover sheet for an FBI serial export, referencing original notes from an interview conducted on November 16, 2010. The notes contain contact information for Jeffrey Epstein's associates and employees, written out by an assistant.

events.title: Interview of an individual regarding Epstein associates
events.description: An interview was conducted, likely by law enforcement, regarding contact information for Jeffrey Epstein's associates and employees. The notes from this interview were written out by an assistant.

keyFacts: An interview was conducted on November 16, 2010, as part of the investigation into Jeffrey Epstein.
The interview produced contact information for Epstein's associates and employees.
The information was written out by an assistant, suggesting it was provided by a witness or source close to Epstein's circle.
The document is a cover sheet for an FBI serial export, indicating it is part of official law enforcement records.
The document's classification is (U//FOUO) - Unclassified//For Official Use Only.
